                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77/932: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé in Russia</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_CF1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Cole</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-07-12T19:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 12, 1919, 7 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>710. Department understands Provisional Government is urging the retention at
                    Archangel of two companies of American Engineers. If so, what are your
                    views.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_PFL">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
